Tightlong junction is useful when you need non-collision junxtion and you don't have too much vertical space.

[[File:en/Community/Junctionary/Tightlong.jpeg|frame|none|Transmogrified junction]]

==Pros==
* Fast.
* Handle up to 8 trains.
* Small vertical space

==Cons==
* Takes large horizontal space.


